@{
    ViewData["Title"] = "Privacy";
}

<div class="container py-4">

    <h1 class="fw-bold mb-4">Privacy</h1>

    <p class="lead">
        This Healthcare IT Ticketing System is a portfolio demonstration project
        created to showcase full-stack web development using ASP.NET Core MVC.
    </p>

    <hr />

    <h4>Demo Application</h4>

    <p>
        This website is intended for demonstration and educational purposes only.
        It is not connected to any real healthcare organization, electronic health
        record (EHR) system, or patient database.
    </p>

    <h4>Information Entered</h4>

    <p>
        Any tickets created within this application are sample demonstration data.
        Please do not enter real patient information, personal information, or
        confidential healthcare data.
    </p>

    <h4>Data Storage</h4>

    <p>
        Ticket information is stored only for demonstration purposes and may be
        modified or reset at any time using the Restore Demo Data feature.
    </p>

    <h4>Security</h4>

    <p>
        Basic input validation has been implemented to help maintain a professional
        demonstration environment. This project is not intended for production use.
    </p>

    <h4>Contact</h4>

    <p>
        This project was developed by <strong>Tanisha Cephas</strong> as part of
        a professional software development portfolio.
    </p>

</div>